The Soppressata ($10.50), with tomato sauce, pancetta, soppressata, onion, mozzarella, and onion might be the best of the lot.  It tastes and chews like fresh baked bread.  It tastes and chews like fresh baked bread. So basically, you should check them out, if only to see yet another wonderful offering in the world of great Philadelphia pizza. must be come back.
